Repository License And Provenance Boundary

Copyright (c) 2020-2026 Blake Davis, Ang Ji, Bichen Liu, David M.
Levinson, and repository contributors

This repository is a mixed research package. It contains adapted NetLogo
Traffic 2 Lanes model files plus repository documentation and metadata. The
license boundaries below apply only to materials that the paper authors or
repository maintainers have rights to license. They do not relicense the
publication PDF, the NetLogo software/runtime, original third-party model
library content beyond its stated terms, source folders outside this package,
or other third-party materials.

## NetLogo Model Files: CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 Boundary

The files under `code/netlogo/` are adapted from the NetLogo Traffic 2 Lanes
model and retain embedded copyright and license notices for Uri Wilensky and
the Center for Connected Learning and Computer-Based Modeling.

Those `.nlogo` model files, including the paper-specific additions and
modifications to the extent controlled by the paper authors or repository
maintainers, are made available under the same Creative Commons
Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 3.0 License (CC BY-NC-SA 3.0) boundary
preserved in the model files:

https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/

Commercial licensing for the underlying Traffic 2 Lanes model, if needed,
must be obtained from the original rights holder identified in the embedded
model notices. This repository does not grant a separate permissive software
license for the adapted `.nlogo` files because the documented
noncommercial/share-alike obligation takes precedence.

## Repository Documentation And Metadata: CC BY 4.0

Author-created repository documentation, package metadata, source-decision
notes, code manifests, public reference metadata, package manifests, and
rights-cleared derived package metadata outside the `.nlogo` model files are
licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License
(CC BY 4.0):

https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

## Materials Not Relicensed

This repository license does not apply to:

- The publication PDF under `paper/`, which retains its publication and
  article-license terms.
- The original NetLogo Traffic 2 Lanes model content except under its embedded
  CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 terms and any commercial-license option stated there.
- The NetLogo software/runtime, NetLogo model library, application metadata,
  or vendor/runtime/file-format structures.
- Zero-byte Dropbox placeholders, local source folders outside this staged
  package, excluded manuscript/figure files, raw simulation outputs if later
  found, and other third-party or externally controlled materials.

## Data Boundary

No data files are staged in this repository. The package contains NetLogo
model files, repository documentation/metadata, and a local paper reference
copy only.
